    "body": "![screen shot 2014-01-21 at 1 14 30 pm](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/831341/1968319/0a00d95a-82e1-11e3-8b95-0da149562562.png)\nFrom top to bottom the sequence in the legend is ABC, but the sequence in the bar segments is CBA. I don't have a strong opinion about which sequence is correct, but I definitely think there should be consistency between the sequence in the bars and the sequence in the legend.\n"
